    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a pure virtual base class for accessing and handling synapses. It provides a uniform interface so that all classes that use synapses can do so without duplication. The derived classes have the responsibility of handling the synaptic events as well as possible return events from the parent. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
